# .specify/ggen-product.ttl
#
# GENERATED-BY-HAND (not `ggen sync`) — a product-mirror ontology asserting facts
# about ggen's own real command surface, FM-* diagnostic codes, and pipeline stages.
# Every individual below is verified against a real file:line citation at the time
# this file was written (2026-07-19). Conformance is enforced by the Chicago-TDD test
# crates/ggen-engine/tests/product_mirror_conformance.rs, which re-scans the cited
# source files at test time and asserts two-way equality against this file.
#
# Do NOT hand-add an individual here without a matching real source occurrence —
# the conformance test will fail closed (TTL-only drift) if you do.

